name: Unsolicited Advice with Ashley and Taryne

episodes.title: Was I in a Cult?
episodes.description: Unfortunately, a lot of people have had a negative church experience. Today we'll be talking about church hurt and how to heal as an adult. Finding a comfortable and supportive community is crucial in maintaining your faith while healing from a broken system.
